@startuml UC_PlaceOrder_Sequence
title Place Order

actor "Customer" as User

participant "Web Client" as WebClient
participant "Orders API" as OrdersAPI

User -> WebClient: open order page
WebClient --> User: show current cart and order form

loop edit cart (add/remove/change options)
  User -> WebClient: change cart contents
  WebClient -> OrdersAPI: fetch price preview
  OrdersAPI --> WebClient: price summary
  WebClient --> User: update cart view and totals
end

User -> WebClient: confirm order
WebClient -> OrdersAPI: place order
OrdersAPI --> WebClient: created order data
WebClient --> User: show order confirmation

@enduml
